# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your own value, then rebuild.
#
# Lume drives your running Spotify desktop app via the Spotify Web API, so each
# person needs their OWN Spotify app (dev mode is per-developer, max 5 users):
#   1. https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard  →  Create app  →  use "Web API"
#   2. Add redirect URI (IP form, not localhost):  http://127.0.0.1:8888/callback
#   3. Settings → User Management → add your own Spotify account email (Premium)
#   4. Copy the Client ID below.
#
# This is baked into the binary at build time. It is NOT a secret (PKCE has no
# client secret), but it must be your own.
LUME_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here
